snippet.title: Pikmin 2 Power Cut Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Yes it coming out 4 days early.
To play join my server.
Pikmin 2 Power-Cut is an pikmin 2 mod/hack where you get energy to recover the energy owed by the presidents wife.

Discord link:https://discord.gg/E8YTkCtuXS
